title: HOUR 3 - Deshaun Watson, CFB Playoff, Nate Newton
itunes:title: HOUR 3 - Deshaun Watson, CFB Playoff, Nate Newton
description:
In hour 3, Colin reacts to the 11 game suspension the NFL and Deshaun Watson has agreed to. Colin also gives his take on why its important for the NCAAF Playoff to expand. And Nate Newton aka "The Kitchen" joined to about the Dallas Cowboys and more NFL.
